IN RE: Marsha M. GREEN NO. 2018-OB-1015 Supreme Court of Louisiana. June 25, 2018

ORDER

Considering the Petition for Voluntary Resignation from the Practice of Law filed by petitioner, Marsha M. Green, IT IS ORDERED that the petition of Marsha M. Green, Louisiana Bar Roll number 17993, seeking to voluntarily resign from the practice of law in the State of Louisiana pursuant to Supreme Court Rule XVIII, § 5 be and is hereby granted.
